# Auto-commit and server update

- **After code changes:** Stage all changed files, commit with a clear message (e.g. in English) and push to `origin`.
- **After a push:**
  1. Update server: `ssh nancy "cd ~/paperless-duplicate-search && git pull && docker-compose down && docker-compose up -d --build"`
  2. **Check:** On nancy run: `curl -s http://127.0.0.1:8023/api/ping` (expect: `{"ok":true}`). Optional: `curl -s -X POST http://127.0.0.1:8023/api/duplicates/start` and `curl -s http://127.0.0.1:8023/api/duplicates/status` – status should show "running" or "done". Report briefly to the user (e.g. “Ping OK”, “Start/Status OK” or error).
- App URL: http://10.23.42.21:8023
